{"tid":1786404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下架抗爭地圖惹「向中國叩頭」爭議 蘋果阻股東人權政策投票失敗","createTime":"2019-12-17T06:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T08:41:52.000Z","uid":303462,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3cab02ef8a0dca807a13d1db6c9f14dbc1404fbc","tid":1786404,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"蘋果在10月決定將「抗爭地圖」香港互動地圖軟件「HKmap.live」手機應用程式下架，引發限制言論自由爭議，消費者組織SumOfUs提出決議案要求他們在股東大會上投票，決定蘋果應否改變其人權政策，及蘋果應否為尊重言論自由作出承諾，蘋果企圖藉美國證券交易委員會（US Securities and Exchange Commission）阻止議案但失敗，股東明年將就相關問題投票。<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191217&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60386246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191217%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60386246&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0gwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=22750555\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191217%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60386246&h=5978d095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191217&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60386246</a><br />\n<br />\n算係少少好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ecde99688068bd92e1cb0c2c32376a75ae9544","tid":1786404,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"蘋果真係奶共奶到呢....."},{"pid":"446185e6cafb144a09f55217f095e731bbdc9f7b","tid":1786404,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6838ed40856be6bf28afdf693f024cce22cab333","tid":1786404,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k